es/2018/08/18/1502652-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F1502652-XXL.jpg&h=44c694bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「毒龍絕技」攬客<br />\n <br />\n2名女高職生去年暑假找打工時，意外應徵到應召站的工作，隨後她們緊急想辦法脫身報警。之後警方前往該處攻堅時，發現裡面大多是越南女子來台賣淫，為了吸引客人，還主打雙飛、輕功、毒龍等獨門絕技吸引客人，甚至可以依照嫖客需求，讓他們自由勾選喜歡的小姐類型和招數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/24/1752231-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F24%2F1752231-XXL.jpg&h=f08beb37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高價位玩到爽<br />\n <br />\n不少色情業者會打出超低價吸引嫖客，但日前移民署北區事務大隊機動隊在網路巡邏時，發現有應召集團招募大陸及泰國籍女子利用自由行觀光機會，讓她們來台賣淫。而警方深入集團內部搜索時，發現其中一名身材火辣女子是裡面的紅牌「G奶蜜桃」，且該集團還主打加價無套性交易、大玩SM性虐待，配合度超高的服務也讓價格高達7800元。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"小弟才疏學淺， 請問乜嘢 叫做輕功呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"輕功：休迅飛鳧，飄忽若神。凌波微步，羅襪生塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"你可以將黑牌當閃使用或打出"},{"pid":"eaa79ad60fbea3fc88fc8e7e554e87ed6b0c6e44","tid":995314,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b937460a570256751717c64b0550f433acb746e8","tid":995314,"uid":103230,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/08/18/1502652-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F1502652-XXL.jpg&h=4541bc0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點車仔面咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"填c 咁on9<br />\n梗係g 啦"},{"pid":"26c5cf07d070f239aefe8f2feea2d21d1224afa6","tid":995314,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b937460a570256751717c64b0550f433acb746e8","tid":995